OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FHeathrow has revealed annual profits
OL,8,Ffell by more than a third, but it paid
OL,9,Fout dividends to shareholders for the
OL,10,Ffirst time in five years despite the
OL,11,Fearnings drop.
OL,13,FOwners of the airport reported pre-tax
OL,14,Fprofits of #575 million for 2025, down
OL,15,F37.3% from #917 million in 2024.
OL,17,FHeathrow's board decided to pay
OL,18,Fdividends to shareholders totalling
OL,19,F#550 million during the last financial
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
