PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FThe airport's owners largely consist
OL,8,Fof overseas investors, led by private
OL,9,Fequity giant Ardian and the sovereign
OL,10,Fwealth funds of Qatar and Saudi Arabia.
OL,12,FHeathrow saw a 0.7% rise in annual
OL,13,Fpassengers travelling through its
OL,14,Fterminals to a record 84.5 million.
OL,16,FRevenues increased by 1.8% to #3.62
OL,17,Fbillion and underlying earnings were
OL,18,Fflat at #2.03 billion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
