OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FHeathrow said the financial benefit of
OL,8,Fhigher passenger numbers last year was
OL,9,Foffset by a number of factors.
OL,11,FThese include lower airport charges
OL,12,Fset by regulator the Civil Aviation
OL,13,FAuthority, increased costs to maintain
OL,14,Fits "ageing" infrastructure and
OL,15,Fexpenditure needed to support
OL,16,Foperational performance.
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@LO]
