PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FThomas Woldbye, chief executive of
OL,8,FHeathrow, said: "Last year everyone at
OL,9,FHeathrow rallied behind our ambition
OL,10,Fto deliver exceptional operational
OL,11,Fperformance for our customers.
OL,13,F"Not only did we meet that goal, we
OL,14,Fsurpassed it and achieved record-
OL,15,Fbreaking service levels.
OL,17,F"With strong foundations in place and
OL,18,Fwith the airport now operating very
OL,19,Fclose to capacity, the next chapter is
OL,20,Fcrucial to our success.
OL,26,@pD@QOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
