OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,F"Expansion will unlock significant
OL,8,Feconomic benefits and create an
OL,9,Fextraordinary airport, fit for the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,F"In 2026, we'll continue progressing
OL,13,Four plans so we can deliver for both
OL,14,Four customers and for the country."
OL,16,FHeathrow said it made investments
OL,17,Ftotalling #1.3 billion last year,
OL,18,Fwhich were "targeted in areas that
OL,19,Fmatter most to passengers and
OL,20,Fairlines".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@cO]zD@LOU|D@IO]
