CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FThis included completing the roll out
OL,8,Fof next generation scanners which
OL,9,Fenable passengers to keep liquids and
OL,10,Flaptops in their bags when they pass
OL,11,Fthrough security.
OL,13,FThe airport said this has "transformed
OL,14,Fthe security experience" by "reducing
OL,15,Fqueuing and improving resilience".
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@XO]vD@]OUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
