PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772025561
OL,3,CHeathrow pays out #550m to
OL,4,Cshareholders despite profits plunging
OL,5,Cby a third
OL,7,FHeathrow is planning to invest the
OL,8,Fsame amount this year, which will
OL,9,Finclude starting work to revamp
OL,10,FTerminal 4, making progress with
OL,11,Fdesigning a new baggage system for
OL,12,FTerminal 2, and improvements to
OL,13,Fservices for passengers with
OL,14,Faccessibility needs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
